        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>David Dorn Back the Blue Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Justice (DOJ) to provide programs to support the hiring and retention of law enforcement personnel and to increase their salaries. Further, DOJ may make grants to state and local law enforcement agencies for this purpose.</p>]]></text>
